<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Luxurious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Luxurious,</orth> lustful, unchaste: <cit><quote>she knows the heat of a l. bed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou damned and l. mountain goat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.4.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 4, 20</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the dissembling l. drab,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.4.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 4, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>l. woman,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 1, 88</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bloody, l., avaricious,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 58</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>